MEASURE_FOLDER = os.path.join(EXP_FOLDER, 'testPAVaryingCATampl')
df = get_data_frame(MEASURE_FOLDER)
df.dropna(inplace=True)

dfc=df.copy()

df_grouped = df.groupby(by='cat_AOM_ampl')
min_ratios = df_grouped['ratio'].min()

groups = dict(list(df_grouped))
dfs = [df for df in groups.values()]

max_freqs = [384182.6]*len(dfs)
zipped_data = list(zip(dfs, max_freqs))
fig, ax = plt.subplots()
for i, (df, max_freq)  in enumerate(zipped_data[:]):
    data = df.dropna()
    freqs = ((max_freq-PUMP_FREQUENCY)-(data['tempV']-data['tempV'].min())*FREQVSVOLT- (data['currV']-data['currV'].min())*FREQVSCURR)
    ax=plot_spline_fit(ax, x=freqs, y=data['ratio'], yerr=data['ratioErr'],
                       scolor=f'C{i}', mfc=f'C{i}',color=f'C{i}', s=0.0, ms=5, figsize=(10, 10), 
                       label=f"CAT Amplitude = { df.iloc[10]['cat_AOM_ampl'] :.2f}", 
                       linewidth=2.5)

plt.legend()

plt.savefig(os.path.join(MEASURE_FOLDER, 'lossFeatures.png'))

df = get_data_frame(MEASURE_FOLDER)
df.dropna(inplace=True)

dfc=df.copy()

df_grouped = df.groupby(by='pump_AOM_freq')
min_ratios = df_grouped['ratio'].min()

groups = dict(list(df_grouped))
dfs = [df for df in groups.values()]

max_freqs = [384182.6]*len(dfs)
zipped_data = list(zip(dfs, max_freqs))
fig, ax = plt.subplots()
for i, (df, max_freq)  in enumerate(zipped_data[:]):
    data = df.dropna()
    freqs = ((max_freq-PUMP_FREQUENCY)-(data['tempV']-data['tempV'].min())*FREQVSVOLT- (data['currV']-data['currV'].min())*FREQVSCURR)
    ax=plot_spline_fit(ax, x=freqs, y=data['ratio'], yerr=data['ratioErr'],
                       scolor=f'C{i}', mfc=f'C{i}',color=f'C{i}', s=0.0, ms=5, figsize=(10, 10), 
                       label=fr"$\delta=$ = {180-2* df.iloc[10]['pump_AOM_freq'] :.2f}", 
                       linewidth=2.5)

plt.legend()

plt.savefig(os.path.join(MEASURE_FOLDER, 'lossFeatures.png'))

df = get_data_frame(MEASURE_FOLDER)
df.dropna(inplace=True)

dfc=df.copy()

df_grouped = df.groupby(by='cat_AOM_ampl')
min_ratios = df_grouped['ratio'].min()

groups = dict(list(df_grouped))
dfs = [df for df in groups.values()]

max_freqs = [384182.6]*len(dfs)
zipped_data = list(zip(dfs, max_freqs))
fig, ax = plt.subplots()
for i, (df, max_freq)  in enumerate(zipped_data[:]):
    data = df.dropna()
    freqs = ((max_freq-PUMP_FREQUENCY)-(data['tempV']-data['tempV'].min())*FREQVSVOLT- (data['currV']-data['currV'].min())*FREQVSCURR)
    ax=plot_spline_fit(ax, x=freqs, y=data['ratio'], yerr=data['ratioErr'],
                       scolor=f'C{i}', mfc=f'C{i}',color=f'C{i}', s=0.0, ms=5, figsize=(10, 10), 
                       label=f"CAT Amplitude = { df.iloc[10]['cat_AOM_ampl'] :.2f}", 
                       linewidth=2.5)

plt.legend()

plt.savefig(os.path.join(MEASURE_FOLDER, 'lossFeatures.png'))
